<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3449119>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Phloiotrya subtilis (KZM): a—dorsal habitus; b—fragment of surface of the disc of pronotum; c—left lateral view of frontal part of habitus; d—aedeagus; e—ninth sternite and tergite joined (dorsal view); f—eighth abdominal tergite (dorsal view, flattened); g—eighth abdominal sternite (dorsal view, flattened). Scale bar = 1 mm (Figs. a–c); 0.2 mm (Fig. b); 0.5 mm (Figs. d–g)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3449119/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

